quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  28,85,"Toto ulia wakhulomesia okhuloonda Ikurani alikhukalusia habundu wokhukalukha. Boola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi amanyile muno ulia wetsa khubulunjifu nende ulia uli mubukori bulolekha.”"
  28,86,"Ne ewe shiwali noosubilanga mbu olirererwa Eshitabu shino tawe, halali nitsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi. Kho olakhatema waba omukhonyi wa abakhayi tawe."
  28,87,"Ne toto balakhatemaa okhukhwikalila okhuloonda tsinyaali tsia Nyasaye nitsimalile okhufimbulwa khwiwe, ne laanga khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, ne olakhatema waba mubatsokaasi tawe."
  28,88,"Ne olalaama nyasaye wundi halala nende Nyasaye tawe. Abulaho nyasaye wundi owulali Ye tawe. Buli eshindu shilisikha halali obweni bubwe. Okhukhalaka eshina khwoosi khuli khuye, ne ewuwe nawamulikalusibwa."
  29,1,"Alif, Lam, Mim."
  29,2,"Koo, Abandu baparanga mbu balalekhwa butswa shichila baboolanga mbu: “Khwasuubila”, nabo shibalatemungwa tawe?"
  29,3,"Toto khwatema balia abali imbeli wabu, ne toto Nyasaye alabamanya balia abahabwene, ne toto alamanya ababeeyi."
  29,4,"Koo, balia bakholanga amabii baparanga mbu balakhukhaya efwe (khubule okhubaheresia eshinyasio). Nookhubusia eshina okhubii muno khwababusinjia khuno."
  29,5,"Ulia wenyanga okhubukana nende Nyasaye, toto ebise bia Nyasaye bitsa okhuula, naye niye Omuwulili muno, Omumanyi po."
  29,6,"Ne ulia ukhalabana okhukhola amalayi, toto yekhalabanilanga omwene. Toto Nyasaye nomuyinda khubiloonje bioosi."